PrecisAppointment of SIMON COAKELEY of Ottawa, Ontario, to be part-time member of the Management Advisory Board for the Royal Canadian Mounted Police, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years; and his designation as Vice-Chairperson of the Management Advisory Board for the Royal Canadian Mounted Police.
